Feb 1 (Reuters) - Wattle Health Australia Ltd:
* ‍SECURES FIRST ORDER FROM MACAU FOR ITS NUTRITIONAL DAIRY RANGE​
* ‍EXPECTS SALES TO CONTINUE TO GROW IN 2018​ * GROSS SALES WERE $329,000 FOR THE MONTH. THIS REPRESENTS 35% OF SALES FOR FY2017 AND 61% OF SALES IN DECEMBER QUARTER Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
